caption.text:
Hope to see you at KCON!!

KCON LA 2024 K-COLLECTION booth offers various excellent Korean SMEs products. 
You can check out and purchase various functional products such as K-BEAUTY, K-FOOD, K-LIFESTYLE, and K-FASHION at once, and get various prizes by attending Stamp Event at K-Collection booth during KCON LA 2024 on July 26-28, 2024. 

💟 I will hold a livestream at K-Collection and share the great Korean SMEs brands with all of you on my instagram on July 27th at 2pm
Don’t forget to get your limited BOYNEXTDOOR Goods also! 
See you all there at K-Collection! 

- Period : 7/26 ~ 7/28, 10:00 ~ 18:00
- Location : Los Angeles Convention Center
  LA Convention Center: K-Collection section
- Online exhibition : www.kcollectionwithkcon2024.com
  #kcollectionglobal #kconla2024

caption.text:
last bits of Hong Kong & Shenzhen 🤍
.
1-Finally with @tamsintan
2-On my way to the @casetify HQ in hongkong I couldn’t stop taking photos of the taxis bc they looked so cool
3&4- First fan dinner in Shenzhen :0 I was super nervous because it was my first time but all the girls were so sweet omg😭 (I hope the hot unnie is doing good ifykyk) 
5- girls sleepover at @fsshenzhen !!
6- thank you for having me @fsshenzhen the meals were FIREEEEEEE 
7- no lash days because it melts off my face 
8-flew back to hongkong for a night and stayed at @hyattcentrichongkong !! They made me a little poster and brought champagne up to my room😭🤍 the meal from @cruisehk was so good, I usually don’t like tuna but I ate the whole thing :0 
9- they gave me a twin room and I kept jumping between the beds 🧍🏻‍♀️ 
10- finally visited the GIGANTIC fabric market in Guangzhou for @teddyiscalling 🎀 I wanna go back next year with an empty suit case to shop
